      Parameters:
      driveMotorId - SparkMax ID for drive motor
      steerMotorId - SparkMax ID for steer motor
      driveMotorReversed - If the drive motor is reversed
      steerMotorReversed - If the steer motor is reversed
      absoluteEncoderId - Port of the module's absolute encoder
      absoluteEncoderOffset - Offset of the modules absolute encoder
      absoluteEncoderReversed - If the absolute encoder is reversed
